These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, aristoff, fonseca
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, chinese, german
3 different games are played: backgammon, whist, canasta
House: futuristic, art-deco, cottage
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, january, may
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, light-blue, azure
 1. the person who likes azure is the person playing whist##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 3. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
 4. the person who likes azure is on the far right##1
 5. the person playing whist is the spanish##1
 6. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 7. the futuristic house is the fonseca-smoker##1
 8. the chinese is in the middle##1
 9. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
10. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2       |    3     |
| Cigar      | tiparillo | fonseca        | aristoff |
| Nationality          | german    | chinese        | spanish    |
| Game   | canasta        | backgammon        | whist    |
| House           | cottage        | futuristic    | art-deco   |
| Birthday         | january    | may | june |
| Color     | light-blue     | emerald          | azure     |

