3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, oliveros, alhambra
House: palace, futuristic, colonial
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk, iced-tea
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, metal, trance
3 different pets are kept: cat, mouse, bird
1. the dunhill-smoker is the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the futuristic house##1
3. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
4. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
5. the person who growsbegonia is the owner of the mouse##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the colonial house##1
7. the palace house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
8. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
9. the owner of the cat is on the right of the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |         3          |
| Flower         | iris    | begonia     | bellflower            |
| Cigar           | oliveros | dunhill | alhambra |
| House   | palace    | futuristic      | colonial             |
| Beverage   | mirinda | iced-tea     | almond-milk             |
| Music-Genre         | metal  | trance       | gospel           |
| Pet     | bird     | mouse   | cat            |

