4. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
5. the craftsman house is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
6. the person who likes fuchsia is the futuristic house##1
7. the person who likes lilac is the fan of reggae##1
8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the townhouse house##1
9. the person playing billiard is the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3       |
| Birthday         | october  | june     | september    |
