 3. the person who's hobby is fishing is in the middle##1
 4. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 5. the chinese is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 6. the mexican is the person driving the roller##1
 7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 8. the person who growsamaryllis is the owner of the cat##1
 9. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is the dunhill-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Flower      | amaryllis    | dahlia     | balloon-flower         |
| Nationality          | chinese  | italian    | mexican         |
| Transport           | tram | bus | roller          |
| Hobby   | gardening    | fishing      | filmmaking        |
| Cigar   | dunhill     | oliveros     | bolivar          |
| Pet         | cat    | rat | goldfish |

