.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-20::.
City: berlin, edinburgh, hannover
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, tram, subway
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, turquise, azure
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, sunflower, azalea
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, november, october
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, alhambra, bolivar
1. the person who likes turquise is in the middle##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
4. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
5. the alhambra-smoker is the person driving the ship##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is in the middle##1
7. the person driving the subway is the person who's birthday is in november##1
8. the person who growsdahlia is on the far left##1
9. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |      3       |
| City          | edinburgh          | hannover      | berlin      |
| Transport         | subway        | tram | ship      |
| Color   | aquamarine          | turquise        | azure       |
| Flower   | dahlia       | sunflower   | azalea      |
| Birthday           | november           | october      | september         |
| Cigar         | bolivar | game    | alhambra |

 